<dl id="n11080f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11080f">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11080f"> 80(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> in the neck </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: To get (also catch, take) it in the neck (colloq.): to be hit hard (by something); to be severely reprimanded or punished. to give it in the neck: to assault or reprimand (someone) severely (<i>OED</i>). </mm> </dd></dl>
